# VS Code REST Client file to test Ollama embeddings
# Requires the REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
#
# Usage:
# - Click "Send Request" above a request block
# - Inspect the JSON response for `embedding` or `embeddings`
# - Expected embedding length:
#   - all-minilm: 384
#   - nomic-embed-text:latest: 768

@host = http://localhost:11434
@model = all-minilm
@text = The quick brown.


### Embeddings via /api/embed using `input` (alt endpoint)
POST {{host}}/api/embed
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{model}}",
  "input": "{{text}}"
}
